headline: Citizens Unveils Citizens Edge™: A First-of-Its-Kind Credit Card Empowering Middle Market Companies to Scale Smarter
summary: PROVIDENCE, R.I., October 09, 2025--Growth-stage companies now have a new way to spend, earn rewards and manage payments with Citizens Edge™, a new commercial credit card from Citizens. Launched in partnership with Mastercard, Citizens Edge offers a robust suite of features ranging from flexible credit limits and cash back rewards to integrated travel and expense management, secure virtual card options and 24/7 client support.
